title: 116 agricultural leading enterprises identified in Yuyao County (Ningbo Municipal Government)
text: ( Source : Ningbo Municipal Government ) Recently , the Guohui Pickles Factory in Simen Town of Yuyao County has been identified as another leading agricultural enterprise in Ningbo after the examination and approval of Ningbo Industralization
